{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01Efko4V5HhSbT1Xsex7zxrz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HyLU3CDXijjtxeoZ2ADcz9","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/GRILLED COD WITH LIME + GRILLED COD WITH DILL BUTTER.generated.24.txt","content":"GRILLED COD WITH LIME + GRILLED COD WITH DILL BUTTER\n\nRECIPE 1: GRILLED COD WITH LIME\n\nINGREDIENTS (4 servings):\n\n- 4 cod fillets, 6 oz each\n- 3 limes\n- 3 tablespoons olive oil\n- 2 cloves garlic, minced\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- Fresh cilantro for garnish\n\nPREPARATION:\n\n1. Zest and juice 2 limes. Reserve zest and juice separately.\n\n2. Mix lime juice, olive oil, minced garlic, salt, and pepper in a shallow bowl.\n\n3. Place cod fillets in marinade for 15-20 minutes.\n\n4. Heat grill to medium-high. Oil grates thoroughly.\n\n5. Grill cod for 4-5 minutes per side until cooked through and grill marks\n   appear.\n\n6. Finish with lime zest and fresh cilantro. Serve with lime wedges.\n\n\nRECIPE 2: GRILLED COD WITH DILL BUTTER\n\nINGREDIENTS (4 servings):\n\n- 4 cod fillets, 6 oz each\n- 4 tablespoons softened butter\n- 2 tablespoons fresh dill, finely chopped\n- 1 shallot, minced\n- 1 tablespoon lemon juice\n- Salt and pepper\n- Lemon slices\n\nPREPARATION:\n\n1. Mix softened butter with fresh dill, minced shallot, and lemon juice.\n   Season with salt and pepper. Form into a log, wrap in parchment, and\n   refrigerate.\n\n2. Pat cod dry and brush lightly with oil. Season with salt and pepper.\n\n3. Heat grill to medium-high and oil grates.\n\n4. Grill cod for 4-5 minutes per side until opaque and flakes easily.\n\n5. Top each fillet with a slice of dill butter and serve immediately.\n\n6. The butter will melt over the hot fish creating a sauce.\n\nNOTES:\nBoth preparations work equally well with halibut or sea bass.\nServe with roasted asparagus or green beans."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":639,"cache_read_input_tokens":108835,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":639},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d60b2f24-f12f-4cee-a7d7-883c82b4ef21","uuid":"4446e830-b5e7-4f04-a06d-5862ae1ed68d"}
