ll butter and serve immediately.\n\n6. The butter will melt over the hot fish creating a sauce.\n\nNOTES:\nBoth preparations work equally well with halibut or sea bass.\nServe with roasted asparagus or green beans.","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
