{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01EM7jCSPgorS4Dsjvq2Z1rf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HVqQ4adPi96bykLhP5Pz8B","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/POLISH SOUR RYE BREAD : WITH CARAWAY : WITH FENNEL SEEDS.generated.24.txt","content":"POLISH SOUR RYE BREAD : WITH CARAWAY : WITH FENNEL SEEDS (VARIATION)\n\nBASE RECIPE: POLISH SOUR RYE BREAD\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n\n- 2 cups rye flour\n- 1 cup whole wheat flour\n- ¾ cup bread flour\n- 1¾ teaspoons salt\n- ½ teaspoon instant yeast\n- 1¾ cups lukewarm water\n- ½ cup rye sourdough starter or 2 tablespoons apple cider vinegar\n\nDIRECTIONS:\n\n1. Mix rye flour, whole wheat flour, bread flour, and salt in large bowl.\n\n2. Combine water, yeast, and starter (or vinegar). Add to flour mixture.\n\n3. Stir until shaggy dough forms. Cover and let rest 30 minutes.\n\n4. Knead briefly, form into ball, cover loosely. Let rise 12-18 hours at\n   room temperature.\n\n5. Preheat oven to 450°F. Shape dough, place on floured banneton.\n\n6. Score top with knife and bake 40-45 minutes until deep brown and hollow\n   sounding when tapped.\n\n\nVARIATION 1: WITH CARAWAY SEEDS\n\nAdd 1½ tablespoons caraway seeds to flour mixture before combining with\nliquids. Traditional version with warm, slightly bitter caraway flavor.\n\n\nVARIATION 2: WITH FENNEL SEEDS\n\nSubstitute 1½ tablespoons fennel seeds for caraway. Fennel provides a\nsweeter, licorice-like note. Combine both for Lithuanian variation.\n\nNOTES ON VARIATIONS:\nToast seeds lightly before adding for deeper flavor. Either version pairs\nbeautifully with cured meats, cheeses, and pickled vegetables traditional\nto Eastern European cuisine.\n\nSHELF LIFE: Rye breads age well. Flavor improves after 24 hours."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":730,"cache_read_input_tokens":109474,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":730},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d60b2f24-f12f-4cee-a7d7-883c82b4ef21","uuid":"c85c61b9-c05c-4163-a1b2-b0babbecb719"}
