{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_011hjiiM1evq1kkcbr5G95C1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EvGMz4rP8E9GYLtrfHexjg","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/WALNUT TART : HAZELNUT TART VARIATION.generated.24.txt","content":"WALNUT TART : HAZELNUT TART (VARIATION B)\n\nBASE RECIPE: WALNUT TART\n\nPASTRY CRUST:\n\n- 1¼ cups all-purpose flour\n- ¼ teaspoon salt\n- ½ cup unsalted butter, cubed\n- 1 egg yolk\n- 2-3 tablespoons cold water\n\nWALNUT FILLING:\n\n- 2 cups walnut halves, chopped\n- ¾ cup honey\n- ½ cup brown sugar\n- 4 tablespoons butter\n- ⅓ cup heavy cream\n- 1 teaspoon vanilla extract\n- ½ teaspoon sea salt\n- 2 eggs\n\nPREPARATION:\n\n1. Make pastry: blend flour, salt, and cold butter until breadcrumbs form.\n   Add yolk and water. Chill 30 minutes.\n\n2. Roll out dough and fit into 10-inch tart pan. Prick with fork.\n\n3. Heat honey, brown sugar, and butter together. Cool slightly.\n\n4. Stir in cream, vanilla, and salt. Beat in eggs.\n\n5. Fold in chopped walnuts. Pour into crust.\n\n6. Bake at 350°F for 35-40 minutes until golden and set.\n\n\nVARIATION B: HAZELNUT TART\n\nSubstitute 2 cups chopped toasted hazelnuts for walnuts. Toast raw hazelnuts\nat 350°F for 8-10 minutes, rub off skins, then chop.\n\nOptional: Reduce honey to ½ cup and add 2 tablespoons hazelnut liqueur\n(Frangelico) for enhanced flavor.\n\nFLAVOR PROFILE DIFFERENCES:\nWalnut tart is earthy and rich. Hazelnut tart is buttery and more delicate,\nwith subtle sweetness. Hazelnuts are prized in European pastry traditions.\n\nSERVING:\nServe at room temperature with unsweetened whipped cream or vanilla ice cream.\nBest eaten within 2 days of baking."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":663,"cache_read_input_tokens":110204,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":663},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d60b2f24-f12f-4cee-a7d7-883c82b4ef21","uuid":"3bf3eacb-cf60-4354-90e5-257a2d94b608"}
