{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01Hv14xUnwb1nuypBFbYy1Mb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PFW1VDdz8PbTo5ZktJTyg3","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Apple Strudel.generated.24.txt","content":"EUROPEAN BAKING & PASTRIES                           Section 3, Page 156\n\n.156\n\nApple Strudel\nApfelstrudel / Zwoje Jabłkowe\n\nCIASTO NA STRUDEL:\n\n- 2 cups all-purpose flour\n- ¼ teaspoon salt\n- 1 tablespoon vegetable oil\n- ¾ cup warm water\n- Extra oil for brushing\n\nNADZIENIE JABLKO [character break] WE:\n\n- 2 lbs Granny Smith apples, peeled and thin sliced\n- ½ cup granulated sugar\n- ½ cup brown sugar\n- 2 tablespoons melted butter\n- ½ cup raisins (soaked in warm water)\n- ½ cup panko breadcrumbs, toasted\n- 2 teaspoons cinnamon\n- ¼ teaspoon nutmeg\n- 1 tablespoon lemon zest [ink smudge]\n- 2 tablespoons cornstarch\n- Pinch of salt\n\nPRZYGOTOWANIE:\n\n1. Mix flour and salt. Make well in center. Add oil and water. Stir until\n   dough forms [text unclear: possibly \"elastic dough\"].\n\n2. Knead 8-10 minutes until smooth and elastic. Cover and rest 20 minutes.\n\n3. On well-oiled surface, carefully stretch dough thin enough to read text\n   through (traditionally). Trim edges.\n\n4. Toss apples with both sugars, cinnamon, nutmeg, lemon zest, cornstarch,\n   and salt.\n\n5. Brush stretched dough with melted butter. Sprinkle toasted breadcrumbs\n   evenly.\n\n6. Distribute apples and raisins along one long edge, leaving 2-inch border.\n\n7. Using oiled cloth or parchment to help, roll dough tightly into log.\n\n8. Transfer seam-side down to greased baking sheet. Brush with butter.\n\n9. Bake at 375°F for 45-50 minutes until deep golden brown and crispy.\n\n10. Cool 15 minutes before slicing.\n\nYIELDS: One 12-inch strudel, approximately 8 servings\n\nBEST SERVED warm with whipped cream or vanilla ice cream."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":768,"cache_read_input_tokens":111563,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":768},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d60b2f24-f12f-4cee-a7d7-883c82b4ef21","uuid":"b744a600-37e6-455e-b8a7-e16869760415"}
